Package com.aevi.systembar

This package contains a helper class enable and disable the buttons in the system bar.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SystemBarService
    The SystemBarService provides control over the android system bar.
    SystemBarServiceProvider
    The SystemBarServiceProvider class gives an entry point to initialize a SystemBarService

    After the SystemBarServiceProvider is connected, by using the AeviServiceProvider.connect(com.aevi.helpers.services.AeviServiceConnectionCallback) function, a AeviServiceConnectionCallback is returned containing the initialized service.
